question: What are all the different sub industries of Retail industry?
What are the top 10 industries in terms of revenue?
sql: select sum(ZI_C_REVENUE) as total_revenue, ZI_C_INDUSTRY_PRIMARY from `sl-test-project-363109.zoominfo.zi-retail-companies-headquartered-california`  group by ZI_C_INDUSTRY_PRIMARY ORDER by total_revenue desc limit 10;
